r-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=fe18b935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"bc342bb3942047a7f379d38d4b1cf28bc03e6ca7","tid":2063952,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=02fc5f7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=73889414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"61a9d5f35c61572636dde652f28515fa763b6322","tid":2063952,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:10:02.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"14d6bc0ced5d2e1d9e94e47e1cf01f43e8ceaee4","tid":2063952,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3f5xcZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3f5xcZG.jpg&h=1a809df9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d2abf741d11b2128dff891044736b2687c759e8","tid":2063952,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:10:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b042b55ab19f182bb908744ba6ea368185e0c3b","tid":2063952,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:10:23.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排<br />\n</strong>- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"84e018a4df5384f7688888dd91656e933503fed2","tid":2063952,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:10:40.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n區域法院交通：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界</strong><br />\n沙田區：182 [盧押道]<br />\n馬鞍山：681 [盧押道]<br />\n北區：673 [柯布連道], 978 [香港會議展覽中心]<br />\n西貢區：690 [柯布連道]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n深水埗區：905 [香港會議展覽中心]<br />\n油尖旺：104 [盧押道], 905  [香港會議展覽中心]<br />\n黃大仙區：103 [柯布連道]<br />\n觀塘區：619 [柯布連道]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n東區：2 [柯布連道], 25 [柯布連道]<br />\n炮台山：25 [柯布連道]<br />\n南區：40M [入境事務大樓］<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"2a0533fdb602edf289af5358b1732511c759acbe","tid":2063952,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n東區裁判法院交通：<br />\n於「西灣河（嘉亨灣）巴士總站」落車<br />\n<strong>九龍：</strong><br />\n啟德：608<br />\n<strong>港島：</strong><br />\n中環、金鐘：720<br />\nCWB、天后、北角、太古：2<br />\n柴灣、赤柱：14<br />\n<br />\n於「鯉魚灣」巴士站落車<br />\n<strong>港島：</strong><br />\n中環：722<br />\nCWB、天后：2A,2X,77<br />\n北角、太古：2A,77,99,722<br />\n筲箕灣：2X,77,99<br />\n香港仔：77<br />\n海怡：99<br />\n<br />\n另外「西灣河碼頭」<br />\n有船來往觀塘碼頭，但旁邊係水警總部<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"eb2ddf60098d4ba1fdd5955a6e6d1247dd41c01c","tid":2063952,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"66人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba270e5d9caadef02bf00eefc7349526e34228a0","tid